docs/studies/estimator/results.json:555:    "verdict": "Threshold 9 first rejects at least 95% at 1 h; the 6 h case rejects 100%. This supports the gate being no looser than 6 h for this deliberately phase-shifted TLE fixture, but does not validate a real SupGP age-error curve."
